latestIgtvVideos.title: Baking Gingerbread Cookies! 🎅🏼🎄✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
🎅🏼🎄 !!!MERRY CHRISTMAS!!!🎅🏼🎄 
Shourye and I made some gingerbread cookies! (with loads of jokes and laughter)

Ingredients:
1/2 cup butter
1.25 cup brown sugar
1-2 eggs (depending on the size)
Spices (like ginger, cinnamon, clove)
2 cups flour
And a whole lot of love ❤️

For icing:
Whisk 1 egg white (without the yolk) and add sugar + your favourite food colouring! Then decorate your heart out! ✨

If you make these for yourself, do tag @shouryeshahi and me and check out @shosha_kitchen 

#ChristmasBaking #GingerbreadCookies
